title: Ellie's Island Deli
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Please confirm if this place should remain listed on HappyCow. There are veg items on the menu, but may veganize anything or just tell them what you'd like in a wrap. Other choices are few and far between on the Island. Remember to take the plastic bag if you're consuming on the ferry. Formerly named Debbie's Island Deli.
